# Plot CLSS responses over time

Use the longCatEDA package by @longCatEDA to plot individual responses to CLSS between baseline and postoperative time points


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
CLSSPlot1 <- UrinaryMaster %>% dplyr::select(contains("CLSSQ1_")) %>% drop_na() %>% mutate(CLSSQ1_Pre = factor(CLSSQ1_Pre,
                               levels = c("~7","8~9","10~14","15~"),
                               ordered = TRUE,
                               exclude = NA),
                               CLSSQ1_Post = factor(CLSSQ1_Post,
                               levels = c("~7","8~9","10~14","15~"),
                               ordered = TRUE,
                               exclude = NA))
```
